# YOUR CODE HERE
N, M = map(int, input().split())
goals = list(map(int, input().split()))
nutrients = []
for _ in range(N):
    nutrients.append(list(map(int, input().split())))

total_nutrients = [sum(nutrient[j] for nutrient in nutrients) for j in range(M)]
met_goals = all(total >= goal for total, goal in zip(total_nutrients, goals))

print("Yes" if met_goals else "No")
